<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> الصَّلَاةِ إِذَا قَدِمَ مِنْ سَفَرٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ كَعْبُ بْنُ مَالِكٍ:</span> كَانَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> إِذَا قَدِمَ مِنْ سَفَرٍ، بَدَأَ بِالْمَسْجِدِ فَصَلَّى فِيهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٤١٥٦]</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>